llion in Fairy Tail, Sawako Kuronuma in Kimi ni Todoke, and Satellizer L. Bridget in Freezing, and Yukako Yamagishi in JoJo's Bizarre Adventure. Noto was nominated in the 1st Seiyu Awards for her work as Yakumo Tsukamoto in School Rumble and as Masane Amaha in Witchblade. Noto has released several character songs and albums which have charted in Oricon, and was a guest at the Otakon and Anime Expo conventions held in the United States.","name":"Mamiko Noto","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"能登麻美子（日语：能登 麻美子／のと まみこ Noto Mamiko，1980年2月6日—）是一名日本女性声优，大泽事务所所属。石川县金泽市出身，血型O型，身高163cm。兴趣、特长是料理、电影鉴赏、拍照、插花。首次工作是马自达汽车的广播广告，初次配音是1999年动画《爆球连发！！超级弹珠人》的ハスラー・ナミ，同年以《幻影死神》的配角殿村望都正式出道。\n\n就读基督教系高校，在校时加入圣诗队[1]。北陆学院高等学校毕业后，就读代代木动画学院1年，后成为大泽事务所的见习生。在年轻女性声优中很受欢迎。因为太忙，被说成是十分难以会见的声优。","name":"能登麻美子","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"能登麻美子是日本的女性聲優。出身於石川縣金澤市，所屬公司為大澤事務所。","name":"能登麻美子","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"能登麻美子","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Мамико Ното","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"노토 마미코","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"มามิโกะ โนโตะ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mamiko Noto","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mamiko Noto","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SK","iso_639_1":"sk","name":"Slovenčina","english_name":"Slovak","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mamiko Noto","primary":